Package: kmermods
Type: Package
Title: Represents Kmers As Integers Along The Genome
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-11-25
Author: Tom Mayo
Maintainer: Tom Mayo <t.mayo@ed.ac.uk>
Description: Scans the genome, turning each kmer into a unique integer. A
    suite of functions for performing swift operations on the integers is included.
    (k-1)mers are calculated, complementary kmers and reverse complementary kmers
    are computed and SNPs can be added.
License: Artistic License 2.0
Imports: Biostrings
Suggests: pbapply
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
